OL,3,CWhat is pre-diabetes and how can it be
OL,4,Ctreated?
OL,6,FEarly intervention work, including
OL,7,Ftaking part in the Healthier You NHS
OL,8,FDiabetes Prevention Programme, is now
OL,9,Fsomething that is available after a
OL,10,Freferral from the GP.
OL,12,FPeople can choose between a face-to-
OL,13,Fface group or a digital service. In
OL,14,Fthe group, they receive personalised
OL,15,Fsupport to manage their weight, eat
OL,16,Fmore healthily and be more physically
OL,17,Factive.
