OL,3,CWhat is pre-diabetes and how can it be
OL,4,Ctreated?
OL,6,FThe digital service uses tools such as
OL,7,Fwearable technologies that monitor
OL,8,Flevels of exercise, apps where users
OL,9,Fcan access health coaches, online peer
OL,10,Fsupport groups and the ability to set
OL,11,Fand monitor goals electronically.
OL,13,FHealth and wellbeing coach, James
OL,14,FBelbin said: "We try and break down
OL,15,Fthe guidance given by NHS England in
OL,16,Fthree areas, 3 pillars. Eating well,
OL,17,Fmoving more and taking charge.
OL,19,F"Each week we will break them down to
OL,20,Fhelp people make a positive lifestyle
OL,21,Fchange."
